data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home that was originally a model home, with open floor plan, bump up counter for seating at the kitchen bar, granite counter tops in kitchen and bathrooms, dimensional shingles, hurricane window protection, new flooring throughout, fresh new paint on the outside and a floored attic for extra storage. Indoor laundry room and a double car garage, along with a covered patio in backyard with 2 ceiling fans.  New sod for both front and back yards and 2 French drains have been placed. Sprinkler system in front and backyard.  The water back flow system has also been replaced recently.  Owners' bedroom has tray ceiling and ceiling fans in all 3 bedrooms.   Garden tub and separate shower in owners bath along with double vanity area.  Underground utilities in this beautiful, gated community in coveted school districts in Pace. Gas is available in the neighborhood. Washer and dryer do not convey.
